---
By: Prabhavananda
Locus:
  Page: 496
  Verse: 19
Tags:
  - Words
---
Try saying “war” or “cancer” or “money” ten thousand times, and you will
find that your whole mood has been changed and colored by the associations
connected with the word. Similarly, the name of God will change the climate
of your mind. It cannot do otherwise.
